<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h4 id="textarea" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#textarea"><span>Textarea</span></a></h4>
<p>Het <code v-pre>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> element wordt gebruik om een multi-line inputveld weer te geven.</p>
<div class="language-html line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="html" data-title="html"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>textarea</span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>message<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">rows</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>10<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">cols</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>30<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></span>
<span class="line">The cat was playing in the garden.</span>
<span class="line"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>textarea</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h4 id="fieldset-legend" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#fieldset-legend"><span>Fieldset &amp; legend</span></a></h4>
<p>Het <code v-pre>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> element wordt gebruikt om elementen in een form te grouperen die samen horen.
Met het <code v-pre>&lt;legend&gt;</code> element kan je een titel geven aan de groep.</p>
<div class="language-html line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="html" data-title="html"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>fieldset</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>legend</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Contact details<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>legend</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>label</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Email:<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>text<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>email<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">/></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>label</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Mobile:<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>text<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>mobile<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">/></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>label</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Telephone:<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span></span>
<span class="line">  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>text<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">name</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>telephone<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">/></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span></span>
<span class="line"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>fieldset</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="button" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#button"><span>Button</span></a></h3>
<p>Het <code v-pre>&lt;button&gt;</code> element geeft een klikbare knop weer.</p>
<div class="language-html line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="html" data-title="html"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>button<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token special-attr"><span class="token attr-name">onclick</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span><span class="token value javascript language-javascript"><span class="token function">alert</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'Hello World!'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></span><span class="token punctuation">"</span></span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Click Me!<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="layout-elementen" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#layout-elementen"><span>Layout elementen</span></a></h2>
<p>Binnen in onze <code v-pre>&lt;body&gt;</code> kunnen we nog layout elementen definieren.</p>
<h3 id="header-footer" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#header-footer"><span>Header &amp; footer</span></a></h3>
<p>Een <code v-pre>&lt;header&gt;</code> element omvat meestal de hoofding van de pagina zoals:</p>
<ul>
<li>Een banner afbeelding</li>
<li>De titel</li>
<li>Een navigatiebar</li>
</ul>
<p>Een <code v-pre>&lt;footer&gt;</code> element bevat meestal de afsluitende informatie van de pagina zoals:</p>
<ul>
<li>copyright regel</li>
<li>links naar verschillende informatiepagina's</li>
<li>links naar socials</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="navigatie" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#navigatie"><span>Navigatie</span></a></h3>
<p>Een <code v-pre>&lt;nav&gt;</code> element bevat de navigatiebar van de pagina</p>
<h3 id="een-article" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#een-article"><span>Een article</span></a></h3>
<p>Een <code v-pre>&lt;article&gt;</code> element bevat een deel van de pagina die eigenlijk op zich zelf staat.</p>
<h3 id="een-aside" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#een-aside"><span>Een Aside</span></a></h3>
<p>Een <code v-pre>&lt;aside&gt;</code> element kan twee doelen hebben:</p>
<ul>
<li>Als het in een <code v-pre>&lt;article&gt;</code> staat is het informatie over wat er in het artikel staat maar niet essentieel is.</li>
<li>Als het buiten een <code v-pre>&lt;article&gt;</code> staat is het informatie over de volledige pagina, zo kan het bevoorbeeld links bevatten naar andere secties van de website of recente blogs of een zoekveld, ...</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="een-section" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#een-section"><span>Een section</span></a></h3>
<p>Een <code v-pre>&lt;section&gt;</code> element groepeert informatie die samenhoort en kan verschillende <code v-pre>&lt;article&gt;</code> elementen bevatten.</p>
<h2 id="good-practices" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#good-practices"><span>Good-practices</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>Als je manuele indentatie voorziet, gebruik dan steeds ofwel spaties ofwel tabs maar combineer ze niet.</li>
<li>Gebruik steeds kleine letters voor tags, dus <code v-pre>&lt;img&gt;</code> en niet <code v-pre>&lt;IMG&gt;</code> of <code v-pre>&lt;Img&gt;</code>.</li>
<li>Gebruik steeds kleine letters voor atributen, dus <code v-pre>&lt;a href=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code> en niet <code v-pre>&lt;a HREF=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code> of <code v-pre>&lt;a Href=&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code>.</li>
<li>Gebruik steeds dubbele aanhalingstekens voor atribuut waarden, dus <code v-pre>&lt;textarea rows=&quot;5&quot;&gt;</code> en niet <code v-pre>&lt;textarea row=5&gt;</code> of <code v-pre>&lt;textarea row='5'&gt;</code>.</li>
<li>Sluit altijd je tags af, dus <code v-pre>&lt;p&gt; ... &lt;/p&gt;</code> en niet <code v-pre>&lt;p&gt; ...</code>.</li>
<li>Gebruik steeds relatieve url verwijzigen t.o.v. de root van je website.</li>
</ul>
